org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.parse.spark

Class GenSparkProcContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.parse.spark.GenSparkProcContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NodeProcessorCtx

    public class GenSparkProcContext
extends Object
implements NodeProcessorCtx
    GenSparkProcContext maintains information about the tasks and operators as we walk the operator tree to break them into SparkTasks. Cloned from GenTezProcContext.
